      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in TCP/IP-based internets.  In particular, it defines objects for managing remote network monitoring devices in switched networks environments. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
